    - Colors matched to Player Window for consistency
    - Mana color standardization: RGB(100,150,255) for "Thorne blue"
    - Part of Phase 5 Target Window enhancements
    
    Phase 6 Additions (Feb 2026):
    - Added player weight display (EQType 24/25) centered between HP/Mana gauges
    - Position: X=90-147, Y=20 (vertically centered in gauge area)
    - Format: "999/999" (current/max) in compact Font 1
  -->
